app.title: What you should know before starting
app.text1: The next points are important to know before you start working as a free worker:
app.cyantext: Click on the green 'next' button if you read everything.
subtitle: 1. Your own boss
app.text2: As a free worker you are a freelancer (Without a registration at the KvK).
app.text3: You choose which jobs you take!
